 <style>

    .header {
        text-align: center;
        border-bottom: 2px solid #eeeeee;
        padding-bottom: 20px;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .header h1 {
        color: #333333;
        margin: 0;
        font-size: 24px;
    }

    .content {
        font-size: 16px;
        line-height: 1.6;
    }

    .report-table {
        width: 100%;
        border-collapse: collapse;
        margin-top: 20px;
        font-size: 14px;
    }

    .report-table th,
    .report-table td {
        text-align: left;
        padding: 12px;
        border-bottom: 1px solid #eeeeee;
    }

    .report-table th {
        background-color: #f9f9f9;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: #555555;
        font-weight: bold;
    }
</style>
<div class="header">
    <h1>Monthly Performance Report</h1>
</div>

<div class="content">
    <p>Hi <%= username %>,</p>
    <p>Here is your monthly performance report for your campaigns. Below is a detailed breakdown of key metrics for all your active campaigns during this period.</p>
</div>

<table class="report-table">
    <thead>
        <tr>
            <th>Campaign Name</th>
            <th>Views</th>
            <th>Clicks</th>
            <th>CTR</th>
            <th>Unique Users</th>
        </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
        <% campaigns.forEach((campaign) => { %>
            <tr>
                <td><%= campaign.name %></td>
                <td><%= campaign.views.toLocaleString() %></td>
                <td><%= campaign.clicks.toLocaleString() %></td>
                <td><%= campaign.ctr %>%</td>
                <td><%= campaign.users.toLocaleString() %></td>
            </tr>
        <% }); %>
    </tbody>
</table>

<div class="content" style="margin-top: 20px;">
    <p>We hope this information is helpful. For a more detailed report, please visit your dashboard.</p>
</div>